sentence: This  march  comes  almost  a  month  after  Israel  launched  a  military  offensive  in  Gaza  following  a  Hamas-led  attack  on  the  country  on  Oct.  7,  which  killed  around  1,200  people.
The  Health  Ministry  in  Gaza  has  reported  more  than  11,000  people  have  been  killed  there.
